        "description": "You find yourself trapped above the clouds - in a wardrobe of a mile high building which is still partly under construction. Can you escape? Not everything seems to be working as expected. You might just have to do some construction work yourself or even nick some equipment from the canceled base jump event on the roof...\n\n'EscapeVR: Trapped Above the Clouds' is an 'Escape The Room' genre game in which you find yourself locked in and need to escape. It is the second installment of the EscapeVR series - longer, larger, and more challenging than the first game, EscapeVR: The Basement.\n\nYou have to escape by exploring the environment, discovering useful items, investigating clues, and solving over a dozen challenging puzzles.  You'll need to find your way out of over 800 square meters of space on three different floors in the mile-high building, each different in appearance, environment, and puzzle content. \n\nCan you escape?",
